# Nihanvi School of Dance — Complete Website Brief

## What This Is

**Nihanvi School of Dance** is a Kuchipudi classical dance school run by a single teacher. This website is a **fully private, invite-only portal platform** — there is no public-facing page. The only people who can access the site are the teacher and enrolled students. The teacher manages everything through her dashboard; students access their homework, announcements, events, and payment info through their portal.

The primary audience (students and parents) uses this site **primarily on phones**, so every UI decision must be **mobile-first**.

