## Database Schema

```prisma
enum UserRole       { TEACHER  STUDENT }
enum HomeworkTarget { ALL  LEVEL  STUDENT }
enum RsvpResponse   { YES  NO  MAYBE }
enum PaymentMethod  { ZELLE  CASH  OTHER }
enum PaymentStatus  { PENDING  PAID  OVERDUE }
```

### Models

**`User`** — all accounts (teacher and students)
- `id`, `name`, `email` (unique), `passwordHash`, `role` (UserRole), `levelGroup` (nullable string — e.g. "Beginner", "Intermediate"), `registrationId` (optional link to Registration), `setupToken`, `setupTokenUsed`, `setupTokenExpires`, `active` (bool, default true), `createdAt`
- Relations: `homeworkTargeted`, `submissions`, `rsvps`, `payments`, `registration`

**`Registration`** — enrollment form submission data (one per enrolled student)
- `id`, `studentName`, `dateOfBirth` (DateTime — **no age field, only DOB**), `parentName`, `primaryPhone`, `alternativePhone` (nullable), `address`, `email`, `experience` (nullable), `certificationInterest` (bool), `performanceInterest` (bool), `medicalConditions` (nullable), `signature`, `signedDate`, `createdAt`
- Relations: `user` (one-to-one, optional — a Registration exists before a User account is created)
- Note: Registration has an `enrollToken` and `tokenUsed` tracked on a related record — see enrollment flow below

**`Homework`**
- `id`, `targetType` (HomeworkTarget), `targetLevel` (nullable), `targetStudentId` (nullable), `youtubeUrl`, `description` (nullable), `dueDate` (nullable), `archived` (bool), `postedAt`
- Relations: `targetStudent`, `submissions`

**`Submission`**
- `id`, `homeworkId`, `studentId`, `markedDone` (bool), `doneAt` (nullable), `videoUrl` (nullable), `teacherFeedback` (nullable), `updatedAt`
- Unique on `[homeworkId, studentId]`

**`Announcement`**
- `id`, `targetLevel` (nullable — null means all students), `body`, `postedAt`

**`Event`**
- `id`, `title`, `eventDate`, `description` (nullable), `createdAt`
- Relations: `rsvps`

**`Rsvp`**
- `id`, `eventId`, `studentId`, `response` (RsvpResponse), `updatedAt`
- Unique on `[eventId, studentId]`

**`Payment`**
- `id`, `studentId`, `amount` (Int, stored in cents), `dueDate`, `paidDate` (nullable), `method` (PaymentMethod, nullable), `status` (PaymentStatus, default PENDING), `notes` (nullable), `createdAt`

