## Testing Conventions

- Tests live in `src/tests/`
- All external dependencies are mocked — never hit a real database or send real emails/SMS
- **Prisma mock:** import `src/tests/mocks/prisma.ts` at the top of any lib test. Replaces `@/lib/db` with `prismaMock` via `vi.mock`
- **Mock hoisting:** use `vi.hoisted(() => vi.fn())` for any constant used inside a `vi.mock()` factory (required by Vitest 4.x)
- **Env guards:** `src/tests/setup.ts` seeds `NOTIFICATION_EMAIL` and `TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER` so email/SMS guards don't short-circuit
- `next/navigation`'s `redirect` throws internally — wrap in try/catch or assert on the mock when testing redirect behavior

